- `status_definition_conditional` (text)\
- `status_definition_no_go` (text)\
- `is_active` (boolean)\
- `sort_order` (integer)\
- `created_at`, `updated_at`\
\
---\
\
#### 6.1.5 LaunchCriterionStatus\
\
Instance of a Criterion for a specific Launch.\
\
- `id` (UUID)\
- `launch_id` (FK \uc0\u8594  Launch)\
- `criterion_id` (FK \uc0\u8594  Criterion)\
- `status` (enum: `GO`, `CONDITIONAL_GO`, `NO_GO`, `NOT_SET`)\
- `current_status_notes` (text)\
